cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT. 

The paper proposes a mechanism for distributed radio resource management using multi-agent deep reinforcement learning in wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves decision-making and control, which suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory) as potential categories.
